                    h2 About
            .about__right.pure-u-1.pure-u-lg-20-24
                .container
                    p Innovation is the key to advance urban railway development in Asia-Pacific. The Asia-Pacific Rail Innovation Collaboration (APRIC) is a collaboration platform linking the group of experts in the railway industry.
                    ul
                        li APRIC stimulates the needs to innovate by proofing the benefits of adopting better innovative technologies.
                        li APRIC advances the speed of technology landing through identification of applicable test-beds for prototyping.
                        li APRIC gathers empirical data to improve the fitting of the solutions to the urban railway sector.
                        li APRIC seeks performing and efficient integration of solutions from the planning, system design, construction, operating, maintenance, through to the stage of asset management.
                        li APRIC connects experts in the urban railway sector within Asia-Pacific region to prepare the best-available solutions for the future.
                        li APRIC fosters G2G (government-to-government), G2E (government-to-enterprise), and E2E (enterprise-to-enterprise) collaboration.
                    p APRIC works in the bounds of research, testing, prototyping, technology transfer, and commercialization for innovative technologies that will make urban railway safer, more efficient to commuters and the environment, and offering more satisfying riding experience.
